{"id":602964,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":19}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"151","ytitle":"","mtitle":"悼念赵丹","ftitle":"","authors":["杨仁声"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨仁声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉赵丹同志在京逝世，不胜悲痛。除唁电黄宗英同志，再献小诗以志纪念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"影剧生涯五十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造形象半百多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诸峰群立显银幕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众喜阿丹奇建树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年浩劫身心瘁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三中”方见喜事多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖擞精神寄未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奈何恶魔劫夺走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民锤炼艺术家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术光辉源流长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化展现新生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群星灿烂放光芒。"}]}